{
  "stem": "2133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, I-- I had-- have a difficult time to know exactly where they were-- they were born in that part of the country, but it-- they changed so many times.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't know if-- if-- I believe it was Austria-Hungarian monarchy at that time, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both my-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my [CLEARS THROAT] father was in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he came back very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a-- a-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] what do you call it now?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A veteran.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I had a hard time to get that word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a war veteran, and he was very sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- I didn't know too much about my father, because most of the time he was in the hospital, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in a-- [CLEARS THROAT] they had some wine-- wine business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they had some land, you know, where the wine was growing, grapes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- that part of Czechoslovakia was [CLEARS THROAT] very [CLEARS THROAT] fruitful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the best grapes was growing in that part, in Berehovo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But most of the time, it was difficult, because if you had one bad year and the crop was eaten up by the bugs or something, so you didn't have enough money to pay your taxes, you know.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was kind of difficult, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and as I said that most of the time he was sick, so my-- my mother [CLEARS THROAT] took up [CLEARS THROAT] sewing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, thank you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took up some sewing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [CLEARS THROAT] she-- she was a very talented lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was more like a designer instead of an-- and she was practically the whole [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] head of the family, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT]",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
